      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and there is a small tear in the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but the suspension is getting noisy and it will likely need new brakes and a tune-up in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind putting in a little work to freshen it up.",
