    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total dream. This beauty is in pristine condition\u2014it's been babied since day one, kept in a garage, and looks just as stunning as the day it was first bought. It drives like a dream and is basically as close to brand new as you can get! I'm looking for a good home for it, so come check it out and see for yourself how flawless it really is!",
