      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently held in impeccable, showroom-state condition. Every aspect of this motorcar, from its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, reflects a standard of maintenance that exceeds typical expectations. Mechanically indistinguishable from new, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection. This is a definitive acquisition for those seeking the finest example of its kind.",
      "price": 46500.0,
