      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior still has that new-car feel! It drives like a dream and I've kept up with every single service. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
